M||titl|Early Return from Functions
M||impa|lo-md
M||impa|avoids unnecessary computation
M||tags|javascript, functions, op, early-return
M||tx|---
M|Earl|tx|Return early when result is determined to skip unnecessary processing.
M|Earl|**In|**
M|Earl|tx|```ts
M|Earl|func|us[]) {
M|Earl|tx|let hasError = false
M|Earl|tx|let errorMessage = ''
M|Earl|tx|for (const us of us) {
M|Earl|tx|if (!us.em) {
M|Earl|tx|hasError = true
M|Earl|tx|errorMessage = 'em required'
M|Earl|tx|}
M|Earl|tx|if (!us.name) {
M|Earl|tx|hasError = true
M|Earl|tx|errorMessage = 'Name required'
M|Earl|tx|}
M|Earl|tx|// Continues checking all us even after er found
M|Earl|tx|}
M|Earl|retu|false, er: errorMessage } : { valid: true }
M|Earl|tx|}
M|Earl|tx|```
M|Earl|**Co|**
M|Earl|tx|```ts
M|Earl|func|us[]) {
